1.en: Government price regulation should be a multi-objective system, refined oil price regulation is nothing more than such a system.
1.cn: 政府的价格规制应该是一个多目标的系统，成品油价格规制也不外如此。

2.en: If there had been, the moon would have been covered with an ocean of the stuff several meters deep and Cassini saw nothing of the kind.
2.cn: 如果真有那么多，这颗星球的表面将会被几米深的乙烷所覆盖，但是“卡西尼号”却什么也没发现。

3.en: People close to Alibaba said the Sogou deal had nothing to do with Yahoo China.
3.cn: 接近阿里巴巴的人士表示，这桩搜狗交易与中国雅虎没有关系。

0.en: So, here's my promise. Nothing lasts forever.
0.cn: 所以我在此承诺，没有什么是永恒的。

1.en: Okay come on Phoebe, it's nothing. Monica, come on.

2.en: You heard me. Nothing! There is no secret ingredient!
2.cn: 知道了吧，什么都没有，根本就没有什么秘密配方。

3.en: You know what's the best about being the youngest? Nothing.
3.cn: 身为家里最小的孩子并没有什么好处。

4.cn: 没有什么事物能天长地久。

5.en: Nothing in this Jungle can stand up, to the Red Flower.
5.cn: 在这片森林里没有什么东西能对抗那红色的花。

6.en: Nothing. I left on my own. You what? Dad, let me explain.
6.cn: 没有什么东西，我自己离开的。你什么? 老爸听我解释。

7.en: I have nothing to apologize for. I told you this was a bad idea.
7.cn: 我没有什么好对他道歉的。我就跟你说这是烂主意。

8.en: You can make the video available to the media. I have nothing to hide.
8.cn: 你可以把录像传给媒体，我没有什么好隐瞒的。

9.en: What surprise is waiting in this pool? There's nothing special in this one.
9.cn: 瞧瞧这个水潭里面藏着什么惊喜？这个水潭没有什么的特别的呀。

10.en: Who's focusing? There's nothing to focus on. It's the Statue of Liberty. Right.
10.cn: 谁在集中？没有什么东西可以集中眼力。是自由女神。对啦。

11.en: There is nothing wrong with Jake. Okay? He is all man. I'm thinking even more than you.
11.cn: 杰克没有什么不正常的，他是个货真价实的男人，我担心的是你。

12.en: Nothing that leads you to suppose a man was hanging around the house? I'm afraid not, Sergeant.
12.cn: 没有什么事让您觉得有人来过这里吗？恐怕没有，警长。

13.en: Which is a good thing, when you think about it. Because nothing else bad can happen when she's asleep.
13.cn: 这样也许是件好事，你想想看，她一睡着就没有什么坏事打扰她了。

14.en: There's nothing like the peace of mind that comes with knowing that your kids are safe while you're at work.
14.cn: 没有什么比这样的平和更重要，那就是在你工作时知道你的孩子是安全的。

15.en: Don't you know I would never let that happen that there is nothing in the world more important to me than you?
15.cn: 你不知道这是我绝对无法容忍的么？这世界上没有什么对我比你更重要的了？

16.en: Hey, ain't nothing in the world that can get me down when I'm holding a little piglet. Look at her. It's time. Sweetie?
16.cn: 每当我抱着小猪崽这世上再也没有什么能把我打倒了。看看她！是时候了。亲爱的？

17.en: My father was Charles Kingsleigh. He had a vision that stretched halfway around the world, and nothing ever stopped him.
17.cn: 我的父亲是查尔斯·金斯利，他的眼光远大，能看到大半个世界，没有什么能阻止他。

18.en: Did it work? No. We need a vehicle with more power. Can I help in any way? It's nothing that I can't deal with. Thanks anyway.
18.cn: 成功了吗？没有。我们需要一辆马力更大的车子。有什么需要我帮忙的吗？没有什么事是我解决不了的。但还是谢谢你啦。

19.en: Honey, there's really nothing to worry about. Okay. I'm serious. Okay. Merry Christmas. Merry Christmas. Merry Christmas, you guys. Merry Christmas.
19.cn: 亲爱的，根本没有什么需要担心的。好的。我是说真的。好的。圣诞快乐。圣诞快乐。你们大家圣诞快乐。 圣诞快乐。
